Recomendations:
This is a list of recommendations to make this project better 
(UI, UX, Performance, Security, Architecture, Bug fix, New Feature, ...etc )

// Please make your recommendations as clear as possible with only a few sentences 

// backend
1. divide backend into three modules (api, controller, model) into src
    - api contain the route
    - controller contain api logic
    - model contain dummy users with functions to get user , changePassword
2. use JWT for authentication(generate jwt for each user)

3. hash the password for user

4. make api for changing password

// frontend

1. divide app into views (login, profile)

2. add routes for app

3. activate change password functionality 

4. create changePasswordController

5. check user inputs before calling api

6. fix login and profile design